videos.headline: Bowden Jr. dives into end zone for 54-yard TD
videos.description: Lynn Bowden Jr. finds a hole and breaks free for a 54-yard score, putting Kentucky up early at 7-0.

videos.headline: Texas A&M ties game on quick TD
videos.description: QB Kellen Mond connects with Quartney Davis on a 3-yard touchdown to tie the game at 7-7.

videos.headline: Texas A&M TE catches pass off teammate's hand and takes it to house
videos.description: Jace Sternberger catches a pass that is reflected off of his teammate's hand and takes it 46 yards into the end zone for Texas A&M to take a 14-7 lead.

videos.headline: Kentucky returns fumble 40 yards to tie game
videos.description: Kent Darius West takes a fumble 40 yards to the house to tie the game at 14-14 with 4 minutes remaining.

videos.headline: Kentucky kicker just inches from giving Wildcats lead
videos.description: Miles Butler's go-ahead field goal comes up just inches short in overtime against Texas A&M.

videos.headline: Williams flips into end zone for Texas A&M's win
videos.description: Trayveon Williams flips into the end zone to win the game for Texas A&M in overtime.

videos.headline: Williams describes his game-winning TD for Texas A&M
videos.description: Trayveon Williams recaps his 138-yard performance and game-winning touchdown run.
